data.description: Welcome Home to your charming brick colonial home nestled on a sprawling 4.6 acres, a dream for horse enthusiasts & those seeking a peaceful country lifestyle. This picturesque abode offers a perfect blend of classic elegance and modern updates. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms & 2 beautifully updated bathrooms. The heart of this home is its recently renovated kitchen, with granite counter tops, subway tile backsplash, and new appliances, it's a chef's delight. On the main floor you will find the family room w/a wood burning fireplace, formal dining room, spacious office w/fireplace, and the master bedroom and a den/mudroom.  Upstairs is the addtional 2 bdrms, and bonus room that can be the 4th bdrm. Outside is set and ready for you to bring your horses, no HOA and no restrictions.
